# Leash secret-read demo — render from the repo root:  vhs docs/assets/secret-read.tape
Output docs/assets/secret-read.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1220
Set Height 500
Set Padding 24
Set Margin 18
Set MarginFill "#181825"
Set BorderRadius 12
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set TypingSpeed 1ms

Hide
Type "clear; bash demo/secret-read.sh"
Enter
Sleep 250ms
Show
Sleep 9s
